{"tid":1562012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[全民狙擊CCTVB偽人活動]9月13號晚上8點大本型","createTime":"2019-09-12T00:11:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T10:23:48.000Z","uid":17646,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"238f94456d02cce73e74812662f29bd26f7eb182","tid":1562012,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:11:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">為何要狙擊CCTVB偽人活動</span></span><br />\n新聞部屢次刪改事實之全部,偏僻藍絲<br />\n我地要全面打擊CCTVB收入來源,偽人(所謂親生仔女)每一次出席任何活動/拍攝廣,CCTVB會抽佣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">如何狙擊</span></span><br />\n只需大家係偽人出場時,採訪時大嗌口號影響活動進行,PR會考慮即時腰斬(馬明事件),而CCTVB收入同時會大幅減少<br />\n<br />\n沙田活動已經取消左<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n日期： 13/9/2019<br />\n活動： 大本型『登月「型」中秋2019』中秋晚會<br />\n嘉賓： 谷婭溦、謝文欣、鍾晴。<br />\n時間： 20:00 - 21:30<br />\n地點： 油塘高超道38號大本型空中花園</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只需一百人以上參與就可以成事</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">13號當晚大家唔好帶同雞蛋到場</span></span><br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FQg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=55f5ab51\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nIG: sayno2tvb<br />\nTVB廣告客戶名單 (消費前諗清楚): <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FQg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=6c4f18e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a><br />\n已加入myTV SUPER廣告、產品代言清單<br />\n<br />\nTG 抵制廣告行動組: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FQg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=5bee9b63\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTG 狙擊活動行動組: <a href=\"https://t.me/tvbfucker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftvbfucker&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FQg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=70346777\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tvbfucker</a><br />\nTG channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/shittytvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fshittytvb&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FQg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=5b7d7d87\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/shittytvb</a>"},{"pid":"702a48c3e3f0db0d6774534d665e786476da626f","tid":1562012,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:11:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d3baf78046af0887a8219b17bc0517e1954bd66","tid":1562012,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:12:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"a0b2f773b870405c484eaf78217d255891db5050","tid":1562012,"uid":30582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:13:00.000Z","msg":"已經完全唔睇佢。"},{"pid":"c80929868b90e8c201998ce66f023f8e4f7aae7d","tid":1562012,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:13:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真係要搞返阻擊CCTVB既支線任</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src