lor: red;\">中共還錢 天經地義 券債還港 合理合法</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0pEqbc4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0pEqbc4.png&h=1f16fd8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FQg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=87407262\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond</a><br />\n<strong>SUBMIT左要CLICK 埋VERIFY EMAIL LINK先當簽左</strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國際之間既債務都有繼承義務<br />\n慈禧簽果條辛丑條約 一戰果時民國繼續還<br />\n仲要還到1938年因爲打二戰窮到pk<br />\n去求條約國唔追辛丑賠款先可以停<br />\n既然中共自稱滿清正統承繼人<br />\n呢張債券自然本利點都要還<br />\n唔還既佢講乜差野要用南京條約去收番香港<br />\n而且美國政府係未同中共追還錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjpU2AG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjpU2AG.jpg&h=45a46f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Yes! US</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"781d02f5681936f308a1853e9303fd2d5d324e1b","tid":1562012,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:18:38.000Z","msg":"願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiW8u64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiW8u64.jpg&h=6e2a8a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558977</a>"},{"pid":"3536d3764467b4126edd63edc324b719dd9d3aa0","tid":1562012,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f58d0104fc597d23bc7e173a9e5a1f542d1204ee","tid":1562012,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply