ize: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個係赤裸裸嘅政治打壓，如果想聲援Ali嘅就要喺每一個TVB活動嗌釋放李佳芯！</span></span>"},{"pid":"5d97452b95ef0ec16354c20d8bc2d0a3d0bcae54","tid":1562012,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:32:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只需一百人以上參與就可以成事</span></span><br />\nTG 狙擊活動行動組: <a href=\"https://t.me/tvbfucker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftvbfucker&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FQg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=70346777\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tvbfucker</a>"},{"pid":"c5c46f3f08117030a228c4b25e6c7777ef0d7612","tid":1562012,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:32:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">對準政權 遍地開花</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2D3bRU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2D3bRU.jpg&h=49b546b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXuufm1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXuufm1.jpg&h=98681984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yM2WNBw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyM2WNBw.jpg&h=9433ed2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zasf29R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzasf29R.jpg&h=aca10195&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}